{"tid":2013191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地逾億學生復課　倘符條件中小學生在校可不戴口罩","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T09:32:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dff9f12cc25413adbbc06d7c1f0550afb25cc217","tid":2013191,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"國家教育部表示，截至昨日有1.07億名學生已經復課，佔總數39%。整個教育系統的2.78億名學生，加上1700萬名教職員中，仍有1名武漢肺炎確診患者，有14名無症狀感染者正接受觀察。<br />\n<br />\n教育部應對武漢肺炎疫情工作領導小組辦公室主任王登峰表示，假如符合三項條件，中、小學生在學校可以不戴口罩，包括所在地區屬低風險，確保每位進入校園的人都健康，以及校內做好防控措施，例如課室內要隔位就座等。另外在運動場上亦可以不戴口罩，但前提是人與人之間要保持距離。<br />\n<br />\n王登峰說，停課期間絕大部分學生較少運動，復課後體育課如何安排，要先了解學生身體狀況；而學生回到學校可能未必適應，要做好心理輔導工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1525659_1_20200512140547.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1525659_1_20200512140547.jpg&h=96c05e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525659-20200512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525659-20200512.htm&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=215afa7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525659-20200512.htm&h=78644180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525659-20200512.htm</a>"},{"pid":"063f646e39b651c0914dfaab3602c9bdb49ef4a8","tid":2013191,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"爆到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae7d6813e67c08016345f2628c7119a1a8cebc2","tid":2013191,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"中共今次事係做得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff6bf9ea7f7047a20451989466f36d721fe4811","tid":2013191,"uid":190005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"人口清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d5f34a8360059a49e8348f7f0a9ffda6e0af9e","tid":2013191,"uid":304856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"岩岩有線中國組先話武漢吉林重新封城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a803efd9918d1045d0b53d657433ddb7d622a9ae","tid":2013191,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d5f34a8360059a49e8348f7f0a9ffda6e0af9e","tid":2013191,"uid":304856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"岩岩有線中國組先話武漢吉林重新封城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"到時係中小學大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}